OL,6,FITV News' Helen Keenan reports from
OL,7,Fthe Old Bailey. Warning: This report
OL,8,Fcontains details viewers may find
OL,9,Fdistressing
OL,11,FThree people who tortured, starved and
OL,12,Fbeat to death a woman from west London
OL,13,Fhave been jailed for life with a
OL,14,Fminimum term of 34 years.
OL,16,FShakira Spencer, 35, died after
OL,17,Ffalling under the influence of her
OL,18,Fformer neighbour, Ashana Studholme,
OL,19,F38, her lover Shaun Pendlebury, 26,
OL,20,Fand their friend, Lisa Richardson, 44.
