OL,6,FThe trio were found guilty of the
OL,7,Fmurder and preventing the lawful
OL,8,Fburial of Ms Spencer, from Ealing, at
OL,9,Fthe Old Bailey in December last year.
OL,11,FOn Friday, Studholme, Pendlebury and
OL,12,FRichardson were each ordered to serve
OL,13,Fminimum terms of 34 years.
OL,15,FThe court heard how Ms Spencer was
OL,16,F"treated like a slave", how the
OL,17,Fvulnerable woman had her feet scalded
OL,18,Fscalded her feet and was fed only
OL,19,Fketchup from sachets.
