OL,6,FThe 35-year-old victim went from being
OL,7,Fa "beautiful, happy, healthy" size 16
OL,8,Fto a "gaunt and skeletal" size six
OL,9,Fshortly before her death, jurors heard.
OL,11,FMs Spencer suffered a campaign of
OL,12,Fcruelty and humiliation by her
OL,13,Ftormentors, who left her body to rot.
OL,15,FIt was not until two weeks later when
OL,16,Fneighbours reported maggots crawling
OL,17,Funder her front door that her badly
OL,18,Fdecomposed body was found after
OL,19,Fneighbours saw maggots coming from her
OL,20,Fflat in Ealing, west London.
