OL,6,FStudholme, of Greenhill Road, Harrow,
OL,7,Fwas the leader of the sadistic trio
OL,8,Fwhich included her friend, Richardson,
OL,9,Fof Broomcroft Avenue in Ealing, and
OL,10,Fone-time boyfriend, Shaun Pendlebury,
OL,11,Fof Tewkesbury Road in Ealing.
OL,13,FThe three defendants had denied murder
OL,14,Fand preventing Ms Spencer's lawful
OL,15,Fburial.
OL,17,FBut in December last year, a jury
OL,18,Ffound all three defendants guilty of
OL,19,Fboth charges against them and
OL,20,FPendlebury reacted by clapping his
OL,21,Fhands and walking out of the dock.
