OL,6,FIn a impact statement read to the
OL,7,Fcourt, Ms Spencer's son, who cannot be
OL,8,Fnamed for legal reasons, said: "I've
OL,9,Fsuffered with daily nightmares and
OL,10,Fanxiety over what happened to her, I
OL,11,Fcannot get the horrible image of my
OL,12,Fmother looking skinny and unwell out
OL,13,Fof my head.
OL,15,F"Why were they (the defendants) so
OL,16,Fheartless? What could cause them to
OL,17,Ftorture another human?
OL,19,F"I hope that every day they feel bad
OL,20,Ffor the choices they have made.
