OL,6,FShe would be woken up in the early
OL,7,Fhours to clean the defendants' houses
OL,8,Fand sent on errands to the shops.
OL,10,FThey subjected her to a prolonged
OL,11,Fcampaign of beatings, enslavement,
OL,12,Fcoercion and control, humiliation and
OL,13,Fdegradation over a period of months.
OL,15,FThis culminated in a frenzied, violent
OL,16,Fassault reaching a climax between
OL,17,FSeptember 9 and 12, 2022, from which
OL,18,FMs Spencer most likely died on
OL,19,FSeptember 14, 2022.
